query: Identify new residential areas developed in open spaces within 10 kilometers south of Aaddoussiyeh in June 2023.
sql:
```sql
SELECT ce.id, ce.class, ce.region, ce.startdate, ce.enddate, ce.buildfromzero, ce.confidence, ST_AsText(ce.geog) AS geometry_wkt 
FROM change_detection.change_events ce, locations_store 
WHERE ce.class = 'Residential' 
AND ce.buildfromzero=True 
AND ce.enddate >= '2023-06-01' 
AND ce.enddate < '2023-07-01' 
AND ST_DWithin(ce.geog::geography, locations_store."aaddoussiyeh", 10000) 
AND ST_YMax(Box2d(ce.geog::geometry)) < ST_YMin(Box2d(locations_store."aaddoussiyeh"))
```
